channel.title: Aeonscape
channel.description:
http://aeonscape.org/website/index.html
Probably one of the best old school servers which are very hard to find these days.
Unique and many cool features.
Has some bugs but that's a given since it was only released within the last week.
Give it a try people! If we get alotta players its one of the best servers and most nostalgic!! ;D ;D ;D ;D ;D ;D ;D ;D ;D ;D ;D ;D ;D ;D ;D ;D ;D ;D ;D ;D ;D ;D ;D ;D ;D
